# 📝 Go Task Manager API

A simple RESTful API built using **Go (Golang)** and **Gorilla Mux** to manage tasks — Create, Read, Update, and Delete (CRUD).  
Perfect beginner-friendly project to learn backend development using Go.

---

## 🚀 Features

✅ Create a new task  
✅ Get all tasks  
✅ Update a task  
✅ Delete a task  
✅ Uses in-memory storage (no database needed)

---

## 🏗️ Project Structure

go-task-manager-api/
├── main.go # Core Go API source code
└── go.mod # Go module and dependencies

yaml
Copy code

